headline: eHealth Shares Down 3% Despite Q4 Earnings Beat, '25 View Unveiled
summary: EHTH's fourth-quarter results gain from higher approved members in Medicare Advantage and Medicare Part D plans. It expects 2025 revenues to be within $510-$550 million.
